<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Living in Chongqing: The Ultimate Guide</title>
    <style>
        /* --- CSS Styles --- */
        :root {
            --primary-color: #d32f2f; /* Chongqing Red */
            --secondary-color: #2c3e50; /* Dark Blue */
            --accent-color: #fbc02d; /* Gold/Yellow */
            --bg-light: #f9f9f9;
            --text-color: #333;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-color);
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545063914-1a0c687472a9?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 60vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        /* Cards */
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .card-header {
            height: 150px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Specific Header Colors */
        .bg-eat { background-color: #ff7043; }
        .bg-stay { background-color: #42a5f5; }
        .bg-transport { background-color: #66bb6a; }
        .bg-medical { background-color: #ef5350; }
        .bg-tour { background-color: #ab47bc; }
        .bg-shop { background-color: #ffa726; }
        .bg-fun { background-color: #29b6f6; }

        .card-body {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .card-title {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .tips-box {
            background-color: #fff9c4;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            header p { font-size: 1rem; }
            nav ul { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            nav ul li { margin: 10px 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#eat">Eat</a></li>
            <li><a href="#stay">Stay</a></li>
            <li><a href="#transport">Transport</a></li>
            <li><a href="#medical">Medical</a></li>
            <li><a href="#tour">Tour</a></li>
            <li><a href="#shop">Shop</a></li>
            <li><a href="#fun">Fun</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Header -->
    <header>
        <div>
            <h1>Welcome to Chongqing</h1>
            <p>Your Essential Guide to Living in the Mountain City</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <h2 class="section-title">The 7 Essentials of Life</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
            
            <!-- 1. Eat -->
            <div class="card" id="eat">
                <div class="card-header bg-eat">🍜</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Eat (吃)</h3>
                    <p>Chongqing is famous for its spicy food. The cuisine is bold, numbing, and flavorful.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Chongqing Hotpot:</strong> A must-try. Beef tallow base with chili peppers.</li>
                        <li><strong>Xiao Mian:</strong> Spicy noodles, the standard breakfast for locals.</li>
                        <li><strong>Suan La Fen:</strong> Hot and sour sweet potato noodles.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tips-box">
                        <strong>Tip:</strong> If you can't handle spice, ask for "Wei La" (Mild spicy), though it might still be hot!
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 2. Stay -->
            <div class="card" id="stay">
                <div class="card-header bg-stay">🏠</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Stay (住)</h3>
                    <p>Finding the right location is key in this sprawling city.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Jiefangbei:</strong> City center, expensive but convenient for shopping and nightlife.</li>
                        <li><strong>Guanyinqiao:</strong> Another major commercial hub, popular with young people.</li>
                        <li><strong>Dashiba / University Town:</strong> Cheaper rent, quieter, good for long-term stays.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tips-box">
                        <strong>Tip:</strong> Use apps like <em>Wellcee</em> or local agents to find apartments.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 3. Transport -->
            <div class="card" id="transport">
                <div class="card-header bg-transport">🚇</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Transport (行)</h3>
                    <p>Chongqing has a complex but efficient public transport system.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Metro (CRT):</strong> The best way to avoid traffic. Lines 1, 2, 3, and 6 cover most areas.</li>
                        <li><strong>Didi (Taxi):</strong> Very affordable. Use the Alipay or WeChat mini-program to call a car.</li>
                        <li><strong>Walking:</strong> Be prepared for hills. "1st floor" in one building might be the "10th floor" in another.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tips-box">
                        <strong>Tip:</strong> Google Maps doesn't work well. Use <em>Apple Maps</em> or <em>Amap (Gaode)</em>.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 4. Medical -->
            <div class="card" id="medical">
                <div class="card-header bg-medical">🏥</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Medical (医)</h3>
                    <p>Healthcare is accessible, but language barriers can exist in public hospitals.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Public Hospitals:</strong> Xinqiao Hospital and Southwest Hospital are top-tier but crowded.</li>
                        <li><strong>International Clinics:</strong> Look for "International Departments" within major hospitals for English-speaking doctors.</li>
                        <li><strong>Pharmacies:</strong> Easily identifiable by a green cross. Good for basic cold/flu meds.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tips-box">
                        <strong>Tip:</strong> Always carry your passport when visiting a hospital for registration.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 5. Tour -->
            <div class="card" id="tour">
                <div class="card-header bg-tour">📸</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Tour (游)</h3>
                    <p>A city of stunning contrasts and unique geography.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Hongyadong:</strong> Traditional stilt houses, looks like the bathhouse from Spirited Away.</li>
                        <li><strong>Liziba Station:</strong> The famous train that passes *through* an apartment building.</li>
                        <li><strong>Yangtze River Cableway:</strong> Offers a great view of the skyline.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tips-box">
                        <strong>Tip:</strong> Visit Nanshan (South Mountain) for a panoramic night view of the city.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 6. Shop -->
            <div class="card" id="shop">
                <div class="card-header bg-shop">🛍️</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Shop (购)</h3>
                    <p>From luxury malls to night markets, shopping here is endless.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Three Gorges Square:</strong> Underground shopping malls with cheap fashion.</li>
                        <li><strong>Supermarkets:</strong> Hema (Freshippo) offers fresh seafood and delivery.</li>
                        <li><strong>Online:</strong> Taobao and JD are essential for daily life.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tips-box">
                        <strong>Tip:</strong> Bargaining is expected in street markets, but not in malls.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

             <!-- 7. Fun -->
             <div class="card" id="fun">
                <div class="card-header bg-fun">🎭</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Fun (娱)</h3>
                    <p>The city comes alive at night.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Tea Houses:</strong> Experience the local slow-life culture in Ciqikou or parks.</li>
                        <li><strong>Bars & Clubs:</strong> Jiefangbei and Nine Street (Jiu Jie) are the main party districts.</li>
                        <li><strong>Foot Massage:</strong> Very common and affordable way to relax after walking.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tips-box">
                        <strong>Tip:</strong> Join local expat groups on WeChat to find events and gatherings.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Chongqing Living Guide. Designed for Expats.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
